ou the option to edit your pages from the backend.</p>\n\n\n\n<p>Featuring a drag-and-drop page builder, Beaver Builder makes it easy to build any type of web page in minutes. The page builder plugin has many powerful, ready-to-use content modules you can use right out of the box. In addition, you can customize each module using the easy-to-use toolbar at the top for a unique build.</p>\n\n\n\n<p>As for templates, Beaver Builder comes with over 30 professionally-designed page templates to make the process of building your site or pages faster. The plugin also comes with many other bells and whistles designed to help you fully customize your site. Examples include custom fonts, shortcodes and widgets, pre-built rows, and more.</p>\n\n\n\n<p>For web developers or entrepreneurs who want to build many online assets, Beaver Builder allows you to use a single license to build multiple sites.</p>\n\n\n\n<p><strong>Pricing</strong>: $99/year for unlimited sites.</p>\n\n\n\n<p><a href=\"https://aioseo.com/recommends/beaver-builder/\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noreferrer noopener nofollow\">Click here to get started with Beaver Builder</a>.</p>\n\n\n\n<h3>3. <a href=\"https://aioseo.com/recommends/elegantthemes-divi/\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noreferrer noopener nofollow\">Divi Builder</a></h3>\n\n\n\n<div class=\"wp-block-image\"><figure class=\"aligncenter size-full\"><a href=\"https://aioseo.com/recommends/elegantthemes-divi/\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"rel=nofollow noopener\"><img width=\"700\" height=\"414\" src=\"https://aioseo.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/12/best-wordpress-theme-for-seo-divi.png\" alt=\"Divi is one of the best WordPress themes.\" class=\"wp-image-67333\" srcset=\"https://aioseo.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/12/best-wordpress-theme-for-seo-divi.png 700w, https://aioseo.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/12/best-wordpress-theme-for-seo-divi-300x177.png 300w, https://aioseo.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/12/best-wordpress-theme-for-seo-divi-600x355.png 600w\" sizes=\"(max