y layout you can imagine. You can also customize every element using Divi&#8217;s advanced design settings. You can also customize the pre-built templates, making it easier to build a page. All this enables you to create any type of custom page layout in a short space of time. Once done, you can even save these changes for future use, making your next build even faster. Plus, you can even export Divi layouts from your other Divi installations.</p>\n\n\n\n<p>While Divi is a theme builder, it works with other themes as well. This is great for times when you want to use a different theme but build your pages with the power of Divi. </p>\n\n\n\n<p><strong>Pricing</strong>: $89/year.</p>\n\n\n\n<p><a href=\"https://aioseo.com/recommends/elegantthemes-divi/\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noreferrer noopener nofollow\">Click here to get started with Divi Builder</a>.</p>\n\n\n\n<h3>4. <a href=\"https://aioseo.com/recommends/elementor-pro/\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noreferrer noopener nofollow\">Elementor Pro</a></h3>\n\n\n\n<div class=\"wp-block-image\"><figure class=\"aligncenter size-full\"><a href=\"https://aioseo.com/recommends/elementor-pro/\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"rel=nofollow noopener\"><img width=\"800\" height=\"362\" src=\"https://aioseo.com/wp-content/uploads/2022/06/best-page-builder-plugin-for-wordpress-elementor-pro-1.png\" alt=\"Elementor is one of the best WordPress page builder plugins.\" class=\"wp-image-101340\" srcset=\"https://aioseo.com/wp-content/uploads/2022/06/best-page-builder-plugin-for-wordpress-elementor-pro-1.png 800w, https://aioseo.com/wp-content/uploads/2022/06/best-page-builder-plugin-for-wordpress-elementor-pro-1-300x136.png 300w, https://aioseo.com/wp-content/uploads/2022/06/best-page-builder-plugin-for-wordpress-elementor-pro-1-768x348.png 768w, https://aioseo.com/wp-content/uploads/2022/06/best-page-builder-plugin-for-wordpress-elementor-pro-1-600x272.png 600w\" sizes=\"100vw\" /></a></figure></div>\n\n\n\n<p>Another WordPress page builde