/p>\n\n\n\n<p>Unlike other page builder plugins, Visual Composer allows you to edit logos, menus, sidebars, headers, footers and more. This means you can also create new page elements that enhance the uniqueness of your site.  </p>\n\n\n\n<p>Another advantage of Visual Composer is that it works well with all WordPress themes. This means you can easily switch themes without losing the custom layouts you created. </p>\n\n\n\n<p>And as the name suggests, Visual Composer was designed to offer one of the best visual editors on the market. </p>\n\n\n\n<p><strong>Pricing</strong>: $59 For a one-site license.</p>\n\n\n\n<p><a href=\"https://aioseo.com/recommends/visualcomposer/\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noreferrer noopener nofollow\">Click here to get started with Visual Composer</a>.</p>\n\n\n\n<h3>6. <a href=\"https://aioseo.com/recommends/themify/\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noreferrer noopener nofollow\">Themify Builder</a> </h3>\n\n\n\n<div class=\"wp-block-image\"><figure class=\"aligncenter size-full\"><a href=\"https://aioseo.com/recommends/themify/\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"rel=nofollow noopener\"><img width=\"702\" height=\"402\" src=\"https://aioseo.com/wp-content/uploads/2022/06/best-page-builder-plugin-for-wordpress-themify-1.png\" alt=\"Elementor is one of the best WordPress page builder plugins.\" class=\"wp-image-101358\" srcset=\"https://aioseo.com/wp-content/uploads/2022/06/best-page-builder-plugin-for-wordpress-themify-1.png 702w, https://aioseo.com/wp-content/uploads/2022/06/best-page-builder-plugin-for-wordpress-themify-1-300x172.png 300w, https://aioseo.com/wp-content/uploads/2022/06/best-page-builder-plugin-for-wordpress-themify-1-600x344.png 600w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 702px) 100vw, 702px\" /></a></figure></div>\n\n\n\n<p>If you&#8217;re looking for an affordable Divi alternative, <a href=\"https://aioseo.com/recommends/themify/\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noreferrer noopener nofollow\">Themify Builder</a> is it. Themify Builder is unique in that it comes