ercome that as it comes with a clutter-free interface. You only see what you need to use, making it easier for you to avoid distractions.</p>\n\n\n\n<p>What makes Brizy one of the best website editors is that it comes with over 400 pre-built templates, animated sliders, and many other design tools. Because of this, you can have a professional page in your preferred styling within a few minutes. </p>\n\n\n\n<p><strong>Pricing</strong>: Brizy has a free plan that can take you only so far. For unlimited flexibility, you&#8217;ll have to go for the pro version, which will cost you $49/year.</p>\n\n\n\n<p><a href=\"https://aioseo.com/recommends/brizy/\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noreferrer noopener nofollow\">Click here to get started with Brizy</a>.</p>\n\n\n\n<h3>8. <a href=\"https://en-gb.wordpress.org/plugins/siteorigin-panels/\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noreferrer noopener nofollow\">SiteOrigin Page Builder</a></h3>\n\n\n\n<figure class=\"wp-block-image size-full\"><a href=\"https://en-gb.wordpress.org/plugins/siteorigin-panels/\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"rel=nofollow noopener\"><img width=\"652\" height=\"350\" src=\"https://aioseo.com/wp-content/uploads/2022/06/best-wordpress-page-builder-site-origin.png\" alt=\"Page Builder by Site Origin is a free WordPress page builder.\" class=\"wp-image-100701\" srcset=\"https://aioseo.com/wp-content/uploads/2022/06/best-wordpress-page-builder-site-origin.png 652w, https://aioseo.com/wp-content/uploads/2022/06/best-wordpress-page-builder-site-origin-300x161.png 300w, https://aioseo.com/wp-content/uploads/2022/06/best-wordpress-page-builder-site-origin-600x322.png 600w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 652px) 100vw, 652px\" /></a></figure>\n\n\n\n<p><a href=\"https://en-gb.wordpress.org/plugins/siteorigin-panels/\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noreferrer noopener nofollow\">Page Builder by Site Origin</a> is a popular (and free) page builder with close to 1 million downloads on the WordPress.org repository. While it offers some powerful capabilities, the downside is that it can be a bit complicated to use for beginners.</p>\n\n\n\n<p>Once you get the hang of it, you can use the plugin to reorder rows, move widgets, resize columns, and much more. You can also easily build responsive pages with the page builder&#8217;s powerful drag-and-drop functionality. If you make a mistake, you can save precious editing time by using the undo and redo functions. </p>\n\n\n\n<p>And because Page Builder is compatible with the block editor, you can use your favorite WordPress widgets or opt to use Site Origin&#8217;s custom ones. </p>\n\n\n\n<p>A good alternative to Page Builder is WP Page Builder, as it also offers advanced functionality for developers.</p>\n\n\n\n<p><strong>Pricing</strong>: Free but comes with a premium version that costs $29/year.</p>\n\n\n\n<p><a href=\"https://en-gb.wordpress.org/plugins/siteorigin-panels/\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noreferrer noopener nofollow\">Click here to get started with Page Builder by SiteOrigin</a>.</p>\n\n\n\n<h2>Which is the Best WordPress Page Builder? (Expert Pick)</h2>\n\n\n\n<p>After comparing all the WordPress page builders, we believe that <a href=\"https://www.seedprod.com/\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noreferrer noopener\" title=\"SeedProd\">SeedProd</a> is the best drag-and-drop WordPress page builder with the most customization options. You&#8217;ll get all the tools you need to create any type of web page or website. </p>\n\n\n\n<p>It comes with hundreds of templates, marketing integrations, and the full theme customizer makes it a no-brainer. Not to mention that SeedProd doesn&#8217;t slow down your website unlike some of the other page builders.</p>\n\n\n\n<p>We hope this article helped you find the best WordPress page builder. You may also want to see our <a href=\"https://aioseo.com/link-building-guide/\" title=\"The Ultimate Link Building Guide You Need for 2022\">ultimate link building guide</a>, or see our expert pick of the <a href=\"https://aioseo.com/best-free-wordpress-plugins/\" title=\"16 Best Free WordPress Plugins You Need in 2022\">best free WordPress plugins</a> of all time.</p>\n\n\n\n<p>If you enjoyed this article, we recommend that you subscribe to our <a href=\"https://www.youtube.com/c/AIOSEO\">YouTube Channel</a>. Youâ€™ll find many helpful tutorials there. You can also follow us on <a href=\"https://twitter.com/aioseopack\">Twitter</a>, <a href=\"https://www.linkedin.com/company/76569804/\">LinkedIn</a>, or <a href=\"https://m.facebook.com/aioseopack/\">Facebook</a> to stay in the loop. </p>The post <a href=\"https://aioseo.com/best-wordpress-page-builders/\">8 Best and Popular WordPress Page Builders Compared</a> first appeared on <a href=\"https://aioseo.com\">AIOSEO</a>.\";s:7:\"attribs\";a:0:{}s:8:\"xml_base\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"xml_base_explicit\";b:0;s:8:\"xml_lang\";s:0:\"\";}}}s:36:\"http://wellformedweb.org/CommentAPI/\";a:1:{s:10:\"commentRss\";a:1:{i:0;a:5:{s:4:\"data\";s:53:\"https://aioseo.com/best-wordpress-page-builders/feed/\";s:7:\"attribs\";a:0:{}s:8:\"xml_base\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"xml_base_explicit\";b:0;s:8:\"xml_lang\";s:0:\"\";}}}s:38:\"http://purl.org/rss/1.0/modules/slash/\";a:1:{s:8:\"comments\";a:1:{i:0;a:5:{s:4:\"data\";s:1:\"0\";s:7:\"attribs\";a:0:{}s:8:\"xml_base\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"xml_base_explicit\";b:0;s:8:\"xml_lang\";s:0:\"\";}}}}}i:8;a:6:{s:4:\"data\";s:82:\"\n		\n		\n					\n		\n		\n		\n				\n		\n		\n		\n		\n\n					\n										\n					\n					\n			\n		\n		\n			\";s:7:\"attribs\";a:0:{}s:8:\"xml_base\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"xml_base_explicit\";b:0;s:8:\"xml_lang\";s:0:\"\";s:5:\"child\";a:5:{s:0:\"\";a:7:{s:5:\"title\";a:1:{i:0;a:5:{s:4:\"data\";s:55:\"How to Add Multiple URLs to Your Sitemap (The Easy Way)\";s:7:\"attribs\";a:0:{}s:8:\"xml_base\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"xml_base_explicit\";b:0;s:8:\"xml_lang\";s:0:\"\";}}s:4:\"link\";a:1:{i:0;a:5:{s:4:\"data\";s:170:\"https://aioseo.com/how-to-add-multiple-urls-to-your-sitemap-the-easy-way/?utm_source=rss&utm_medium=rss&utm_campaign=how-to-add-multiple-urls-to-your-sitemap-the-easy-way\";s:7:\"attribs\";a:0:{}s:8:\"xml_base\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"xml_base_explicit\";b:0;s:8:\"xml_lang\";s:0:\"\";}}s:8:\"comments\";a:1:{i:0;a:5:{s:4:\"data\";s:81:\"https://aioseo.com/how-to-add-multiple-urls-to-your-sitemap-the-easy-way/#respond\";s:7:\"attribs\";a:0:{}s:8:\"xml_base\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"xml_base_explicit\";b:0;s:8:\"xml_lang\";s:0:\"\";}}s:7:\"pubDate\";a:1:{i:0;a:5:{s:4:\"data\";s:31:\"Thu, 23 Jun 2022 12:59:49 +0000\";s:7:\"attribs\";a:0:{}s:8:\"xml_base\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"xml_base_explicit\";b:0;s:8:\"xml_lang\";s:0:\"\";}}s:8:\"category\";a:4:{i:0;a:5:{s:4:\"data\";s:4:\"Blog\";s:7:\"attribs\";a:0:{}s:8:\"xml_base\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"xml_base_explicit\";b:0;s:8:\"xml_lang\";s:0:\"\";}i:1;a:5:{s:4:\"data\";s:8:\"SEO Tips\";s:7:\"attribs\";a:0:{}s:8:\"xml_base\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"xml_base_explicit\";b:0;s:8:\"xml_lang\";s:0:\"\";}i:2;a:5:{s:4:\"data\";s:32:\"adding multiple URLs to sitemaps\";s:7:\"attribs\";a:0:{}s:8:\"xml_base\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"xml_base_explicit\";b:0;s:8:\"xml_lang\";s:0:\"\";}i:3;a:5:{s:4:\"data\";s:18:\"WordPress sitemaps\";s:7:\"attribs\";a:0:{}s:8:\"xml_base\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"xml_base_explicit\";b:0;s:8:\"xml_lang\";s:0:\"\";}}s:4:\"guid\";a:1:{i:0;a:5:{s:4:\"data\";s:27:\"https://aioseo.com/?p=99826\";s:7:\"attribs\";a:1:{s:0:\"\";a:1:{s:11:\"isPermaLink\";s:5:\"false\";}}s:8:\"xml_base\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"xml_base_explicit\";b:0;s:8:\"xml_lang\";s:0:\"\";}}s:11:\"description\";a:1:{i:0;a:5:{s:4:\"data\";s:462:\"<p>Do you want to know how to add multiple URLs to your sitemap? Sitemaps are an essential SEO element that helps search engines discover the important pages on your site much faster. However, manually adding each URL is time-consuming and&#8230;</p>\nThe post <a href=\"https://aioseo.com/how-to-add-multiple-urls-to-your-sitemap-the-easy-way/\">How to Add Multiple URLs to Your Sitemap (The Easy Way)</a> first appeared on <a href=\"https://aioseo.com\">AIOSEO</a>.\";s:7:\"attribs\";a:0:{}s:8:\"xml_base\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"xml_base_explicit\";b:0;s:8:\"xml_lang\";s:0:\"\";}}}s:32:\"http://purl.org/dc/elements/1.1/\";a:1:{s:7:\"creator\";a:1:{i:0;a:5:{s:4:\"data\";s:11:\"Kato Nkhoma\";s:7:\"attribs\";a:0:{}s:8:\"xml_base\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"xml_base_explicit\";b:0;s:8:\"xml_lang\";s:0:\"\";}}}s:40:\"http://purl.org/rss/1.0/modules/content/\";a:1:{s:7:\"encoded\";a:1:{i:0;a:5:{s:4:\"data\";s:8719:\"<p>Do you want to know how to add multiple URLs to your sitemap?</p>\n\n\n\n<p>Sitemaps are an essential SEO element that helps search engines discover the important pages on your site much faster. However, manually adding each URL is time-consuming and laborious for large websites.</p>\n\n\n\n<p>This article will show you how to add multiple URLs to your sitemaps easily. And it will only take you a few minutes.</p>\n\n\n\n<h2>What is a Sitemap?</h2>\n\n\n\n<p>A sitemap is a file created to provide information about your website&#8217;s pages, media, and other files. It also shows the relationships between them. Sitemaps are essential assets on a website as they tell search engines:</p>\n\n\n\n<ul><li>Which pages to prioritize</li><li>When a page was last modified</li><li>Alternate language versions of your content (if any)</li><li>And much more</li></ul>\n\n\n\n<p>Sitemaps also help you provide information about specific types of content on your website. Examples include <a href=\"https://aioseo.com/create-a-google-news-sitemap/\" title=\"How to Create a Google News Sitemap (In a Single Click)\">news content</a>, video content, images, and more.</p>\n\n\n\n<p>All this is valuable information that results in optimized <a href=\"https://aioseo.com/docs/crawl-cleanup-best-practices/\" title=\"How to Use Crawl Cleanup to Increase Search Engine Crawl Quota\">crawl efficiency</a>.</p>\n\n\n\n<p>As your website grows, there will be more URLs you must add to your sitemap. Also, when you build landing pages and other assets outside of WordPress, you may want to include them in your sitemap for indexing. This may require you to add multiple URLs to your sitemap.&nbsp;</p>\n\n\n\n<p>Thatâ€™s why we want to show you the easy way of adding multiple URLs to your sitemap.</p>\n\n\n\n<h2>How to Add Multiple URLs to Your Sitemap</h2>\n\n\n\n<p>The first step to easily adding multiple URLs to your sitemap is installing and activating <a href=\"https://aioseo.com/pricing/\" title=\"All In One SEO (AIOSEO)\">All In One SEO (AIOSEO)</a> on your WordPress website. AIOSEO is the best WordPress SEO plugin on the market and boasts over 3 million downloads.&nbsp;</p>\n\n\n\n<div class=\"wp-block-image\"><figure class=\"aligncenter size-full\"><img width=\"700\" height=\"311\" src=\"https://aioseo.com/wp-content/uploads/2022/06/adding-seo-keywords-aioseo.png\" alt=\"AIOSEO is a powerful tool that makes it easy to add multiple URLs to a sitemap.\" class=\"wp-image-96547\" srcset=\"https://aioseo.com/wp-content/uploads/2022/06/adding-seo-keywords-aioseo.png 700w, https://aioseo.com/wp-content/uploads/2022/06/adding-seo-keywords-aioseo-300x133.png 300w, https://aioseo.com/wp-content/uploads/2022/06/adding-seo-keywords-aioseo-600x267.png 600w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 700px) 100vw, 700px\" /></figure></div>\n\n\n\n<p>Smart website owners use AIOSEO to help improve search rankings as it comes with powerful features you need to set up your SEO settings correctly such as schema markups, the ability to build strategic internal links on autopilot, and much more. It also comes with one of the <a href=\"https://aioseo.com/features/smart-xml-sitemaps/\" title=\"Smart XML Sitemaps\">best WordPress sitemap generators</a> on the market.</p>\n\n\n\n<p>By default, AIOSEO will automatically include all your WordPress posts, pages, and custom post types in the sitemap.</p>\n\n\n\n<p>But the plugin can also help you easily add multiple other URLs to your sitemap without having to tinker with any code or technical aspects of your site. This is really helpful if you&#8217;re using WordPress as your main site, but have your store on Shopify or BigCommerce, and you may want to add those links in your main sitemap.</p>\n\n\n\n<p>To get started, the first thing you need to do is install and activate the All in One SEO plugin. For more details, <a href=\"https://aioseo.com/docs/installing-all-in-one-seo-pro/\" title=\"Installing All in One SEO Pro\">check out our installation guide</a>.</p>\n\n\n\n<p>Once youâ€™ve installed the plugin, itâ€™s easy to add multiple URLs to your sitemap, thanks to our powerful Additional Pages feature under the Sitemaps settings tab. To get started so, go to <strong>Sitemaps</strong> Â» <strong>General Sitemaps</strong>.&nbsp;</p>\n\n\n\n<figure class=\"wp-block-image size-full\"><img width=\"700\" height=\"181\" src=\"https://aioseo.com/wp-content/uploads/2022/06/add-multiple-urls-to-sitemap-1.png\" alt=\"To add multiple URLs to your sitemap, head to the General Sitemap section of AIOSEO\'s sitemap settings.\" class=\"wp-image-99834\" srcset=\"https://aioseo.com/wp-content/uploads/2022/06/add-multiple-urls-to-sitemap-1.png 700w, https://aioseo.com/wp-content/uploads/2022/06/add-multiple-urls-to-sitemap-1-300x78.png 300w, https://aioseo.com/wp-content/uploads/2022/06/add-multiple-urls-to-sitemap-1-600x155.png 600w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 700px) 100vw, 700px\" /></figure>\n\n\n\n<p>Next, scroll down the page where youâ€™ll find the <strong>Additional Pages</strong> section. Enabling this feature will open up a window that gives you options for adding multiple URLS by importing a CSV file containing the URLs you want to add.</p>\n\n\n\n<div class=\"wp-block-image\"><figure class=\"aligncenter size-large\"><img width=\"1024\" height=\"345\" src=\"https://aioseo.com/wp-content/uploads/2022/06/add-multiple-urls-to-additional-pages-1-1024x345.png\" alt=\"The Import CSV button will open a window that enables you to choose a CSV file.\" class=\"wp-image-99835\" srcset=\"https://aioseo.com/wp-content/uploads/2022/06/add-multiple-urls-to-additional-pages-1-1024x345.png 1024w, https://aioseo.com/wp-content/uploads/2022/06/add-multiple-urls-to-additional-pages-1-300x101.png 300w, https://aioseo.com/wp-content/uploads/2022/06/add-multiple-urls-to-additional-pages-1-768x259.png 768w, https://aioseo.com/wp-content/uploads/2022/06/add-multiple-urls-to-additional-pages-1-600x202.png 600w, https://aioseo.com/wp-content/uploads/2022/06/add-multiple-urls-to-additional-pages-1.png 1038w\" sizes=\"100vw\" /></figure></div>\n\n\n\n<p>Clicking on the <strong>Import from CSV</strong> button will open another window with a field for uploading your CSV file.</p>\n\n\n\n<div class=\"wp-block-image\"><figure class=\"aligncenter size-full\"><img width=\"420\" height=\"350\" src=\"https://aioseo.com/wp-content/uploads/2022/06/add-multiple-urls-to-sitemap-upload-file-min.png\" alt=\"To add multiple URLs to your sitemap, choose a CSV file to import.\" class=\"wp-image-99836\" srcset=\"https://aioseo.com/wp-content/uploads/2022/06/add-multiple-urls-to-sitemap-upload-file-min.png 420w, https://aioseo.com/wp-content/uploads/2022/06/add-multiple-urls-to-sitemap-upload-file-min-300x250.png 300w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 420px) 100vw, 420px\" /></figure></div>\n\n\n\n<p>After choosing and uploading your CSV file, click the <strong>Import</strong> button. Doing so results in all the URLs in your CSV file being added to your sitemap.</p>\n\n\n\n<div class=\"wp-block-image\"><figure class=\"aligncenter size-full\"><img width=\"698\" height=\"400\" src=\"https://aioseo.com/wp-content/uploads/2022/06/add-multiple-urls-to-sitemap-final.png\" alt=\"The imported URLs will be added to your sitemap.\" class=\"wp-image-99838\" srcset=\"https://aioseo.com/wp-content/uploads/2022/06/add-multiple-urls-to-sitemap-final.png 698w, https://aioseo.com/wp-content/uploads/2022/06/add-multiple-urls-to-sitemap-final-300x172.png 300w, https://aioseo.com/wp-content/uploads/2022/06/add-multiple-urls-to-sitemap-final-600x344.png 600w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 698px) 100vw, 698px\" /></figure></div>\n\n\n\n<p>Once your URLs have been added, click <strong>Save,</strong> and thatâ€™s it!</p>\n\n\n\n<p>Now search engines will know which pages to prioritize as they crawl your site. </p>\n\n\n\n<p>We hope this article has helped you learn how to add multiple URLs to your sitemap. You may also want to see our <a href=\"https://aioseo.com/ultimate-wordpress-seo-guide/\" title=\"Ultimate WordPress SEO Guide: Optimize Your Site in 2022\">beginner&#8217;s guide to WordPress SEO</a> or see our <a href=\"https://aioseo.com/link-building-guide/\" title=\"The Ultimate Link Building Guide You Need for 2022\">ultimate link building guide</a> to improve your SEO rankings. </p>\n\n\n\n<p>If you found this article helpful, then please subscribe to our <a href=\"https://www.youtube.com/c/AIOSEO\">YouTube Channel</a>. Youâ€™ll find many more helpful tutorials there. You can also follow us on <a href=\"https://twitter.com/aioseopack\">Twitter</a>, <a href=\"https://www.linkedin.com/company/76569804/\">LinkedIn</a>, or <a href=\"https://m.facebook.com/aioseopack/\">Facebook</a> to stay in the loop.</p>The post <a href=\"https://aioseo.com/how-to-add-multiple-urls-to-your-sitemap-the-easy-way/\">How to Add Multiple URLs to Your Sitemap (The Easy Way)</a> first appeared on <a href=\"https://aioseo.com\">AIOSEO</a>.\";s:7:\"attribs\";a:0:{}s:8:\"xml_base\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"xml_base_explicit\";b:0;s:8:\"xml_lang\";s:0:\"\";}}}s:36:\"http://wellformedweb.org/CommentAPI/\";a:1:{s:10:\"commentRss\";a:1:{i:0;a:5:{s:4:\"data\";s:78:\"https://aioseo.com/how-to-add-multiple-urls-to-your-sitemap-the-easy-way/feed/\";s:7:\"attribs\";a:0:{}s:8:\"xml_base\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"xml_base_explicit\";b:0;s:8:\"xml_lang\";s:0:\"\";}}}s:38:\"http://purl.org/rss/1.0/modules/slash/\";a:1:{s:8:\"comments\";a:1:{i:0;a:5:{s:4:\"data\";s:1:\"0\";s:7:\"attribs\";a:0:{}s:8:\"xml_base\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"xml_base_explicit\";b:0;s:8:\"xml_lang\";s:0:\"\";}}}}}i: