s:23:\"user social profile tab\";s:7:\"attribs\";a:0:{}s:8:\"xml_base\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"xml_base_explicit\";b:0;s:8:\"xml_lang\";s:0:\"\";}}s:4:\"guid\";a:1:{i:0;a:5:{s:4:\"data\";s:27:\"https://aioseo.com/?p=99213\";s:7:\"attribs\";a:1:{s:0:\"\";a:1:{s:11:\"isPermaLink\";s:5:\"false\";}}s:8:\"xml_base\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"xml_base_explicit\";b:0;s:8:\"xml_lang\";s:0:\"\";}}s:11:\"description\";a:1:{i:0;a:5:{s:4:\"data\";s:495:\"<p>This year, weâ€™re on a mission to add the most value to our plugin. Thatâ€™s why weâ€™re so excited to announce AIOSEO 4.2.2. In this update, we have a lot of exciting improvements, with the top two being: Social profile&#8230;</p>\nThe post <a href=\"https://aioseo.com/announcing-our-new-user-social-profile-tab-and-translation-api-in-aioseo-4-2-2/\">Announcing Our New User Social Profile Tab and Translation API in AIOSEO 4.2.2</a> first appeared on <a href=\"https://aioseo.com\">AIOSEO</a>.\";s:7:\"attribs\";a:0:{}s:8:\"xml_base\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"xml_base_explicit\";b:0;s:8:\"xml_lang\";s:0:\"\";}}}s:32:\"http://purl.org/dc/elements/1.1/\";a:1:{s:7:\"creator\";a:1:{i:0;a:5:{s:4:\"data\";s:14:\"Benjamin Rojas\";s:7:\"attribs\";a:0:{}s:8:\"xml_base\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"xml_base_explicit\";b:0;s:8:\"xml_lang\";s:0:\"\";}}}s:40:\"http://purl.org/rss/1.0/modules/content/\";a:1:{s:7:\"encoded\";a:1:{i:0;a:5:{s:4:\"data\";s:5262:\"<p>This year, weâ€™re on a mission to add the most value to our plugin.</p>\n\n\n\n<p>Thatâ€™s why weâ€™re so excited to announce AIOSEO 4.2.2.</p>\n\n\n\n<p>In this update, we have a lot of exciting improvements, with the top two being:</p>\n\n\n\n<ul><li>Social profile management</li><li>Translation API</li></ul>\n\n\n\n<p>These are features designed to give your SEO a boost so you can get more traffic to your website. The best part is theyâ€™re easy to use, even if youâ€™re a WordPress newbie.</p>\n\n\n\n<p>Letâ€™s quickly dive into what this new update offers for AIOSEO users.</p>\n\n\n\n<figure class=\"wp-block-embed is-type-video is-provider-youtube wp-block-embed-youtube wp-embed-aspect-16-9 wp-has-aspect-ratio\"><div class=\"wp-block-embed__wrapper\">\n<iframe title=\"Introducing Our New User Social Profile Tab and Translation API\" width=\"500\" height=\"281\" src=\"https://www.youtube.com/embed/aO1iAIJQ36E?feature=oembed\" frameborder=\"0\" allow=\"accelerometer; autoplay; clipboard-write; encrypted-media; gyroscope; picture-in-picture\" allowfullscreen></iframe>\n</div></figure>\n\n\n\n<h2>Easily Connect Your Social Media Profiles to Your Site</h2>\n\n\n\n<p>The first feature we&#8217;re proud to introduce is the User Social Profile management feature. It makes it easy for you to connect your social media profiles to your WordPress user accounts â€“ with just a few clicks.</p>\n\n\n\n<p>One reason weâ€™re happy to announce this feature is that itâ€™s one of the most-requested features by many of our users.</p>\n\n\n\n<p>To access this new feature, head over to your WordPress dashboard and click on <strong>Users</strong> &gt;&gt; <strong>Profile</strong>. This will take you to the User Profile page.</p>\n\n\n\n<div class=\"wp-block-image\"><figure class=\"aligncenter size-full\"><img width=\"431\" height=\"400\" src=\"https://aioseo.com/wp-content/uploads/2022/06/social-profile-3.png\" alt=\"The new User Social Profile tab enables you to connect your social media accounts to your wordPress user account.\" class=\"wp-image-99561\" srcset=\"https://aioseo.com/wp-content/uploads/2022/06/social-profile-3.png 431w, https://aioseo.com/wp-content/uploads/2022/06/social-profile-3-300x278.png 300w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 431px) 100vw, 431px\" /></figure></div>\n\n\n\n<p>You can then fill in the social media profiles you want associated with that user. For example, you can easily connect your Facebook, Twitter, LinkedIn, or any other social media account to your user profile.</p>\n\n\n\n<p>Once youâ€™re done, click <strong>Save</strong>.</p>\n\n\n\n<p>This will result in your social media profiles being added to your siteâ€™s schema. Schema is a code that helps search engines understand your site better. Adding your social profiles has many advantages including boosting your:</p>\n\n\n\n<ul><li><strong>Google E-A-T score</strong>: Expertise, authority, and trustworthiness (E-A-T) is a score Google uses to rate the quality of content on your site. Trustworthiness is an important element in getting a good E-A-T score. Connecting social profiles to your content improves the trust factor.</li><li><strong>Entity SEO</strong>: Entity SEO involves search engines using related data about an entity (person, business, or object) to build a better profile. This helps them serve relevant answers to queries related to said entity.</li></ul>\n\n\n\n<p>In short, this helps boost discoverability and results in more traffic to your site.</p>\n\n\n\n<h2>Localize Your SEO Data with the Translation API</h2>\n\n\n\n<p>Our brand new translation API is another reason weâ€™re excited about AIOSEO 4.2.2. The translation API enables third-party translation apps to hook into AIOSEOâ€™s data to translate it easily.</p>\n\n\n\n<p>This helps users reach a wider audience. But more importantly, it helps boost your multilingual SEO. With our new translation API, you can rank for important keywords across different languages and geographic demographics.</p>\n\n\n\n<p>Of course, that translates to more traffic to your website and faster growth for your business.&nbsp;</p>\n\n\n\n<p>Besides these 2, weâ€™ve updated many of the features you love in AIOSEO, such as improved:</p>\n\n\n\n<ul><li>Content optimization</li><li>The pre-publish panel that now includes a check for the social data</li><li>Link Suggestions</li><li>And much more!</li></ul>\n\n\n\n<p>This update has lots of exciting additions and improvements to help your website rank higher, so make sure to update to AIOSEO 4.2.2 today.</p>\n\n\n\n<p>If you have any questions, feel free to <a href=\"https://aioseo.com/contact/\" title=\"Contact Us\">reach out to our customer support team here</a>, and theyâ€™ll be happy to help you out.</p>\n\n\n\n<p>Go ahead and take advantage of the additional power of AIOSEO 4.2.2 by upgrading to a <a href=\"https://aioseo.com/pricing/\" title=\"Pricing\">Pro or Elite plan</a>.&nbsp;</p>\n\n\n\n<p>As always, we value your feedback and input. Thatâ€™s why we encourage you to keep the suggestions and feature requests coming. Together, weâ€™ll build the worldâ€™s best WordPress SEO plugin and toolkit.</p>The post <a href=\"https://aioseo.com/announcing-our-new-user-social-profile-tab-and-translation-api-in-aioseo-4-2-2/\">Announcing Our New User Social Profile Tab and Translation API in AIOSEO 4.2.2</a> first appeared on <a href=\"https://aioseo.com\">AIOSEO</a>.\";s:7:\"attribs\";a:0:{}s:8:\"xml_base\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"xml_base_explicit\";b:0;s:8:\"xml_lang\";s:0:\"\";}}}s:36:\"http://wellformedweb.org/CommentAPI/\";a:1:{s:10:\"commentRss\";a:1:{i:0;a:5:{s:4:\"data\";s:103:\"https://aioseo.com/announcing-our-new-user-social-profile-tab-and-translation-api-in-aioseo-4-2-2/feed/\";s:7:\"attribs\";a:0:{}s:8:\"xml_base\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"xml_base_explicit\";b:0;s:8:\"xml_lang\";s:0:\"\";}}}s:38:\"http://purl.org/rss/1.0/modules/slash/\";a:1:{s:8:\"comments\";a:1:{i:0;a:5:{s:4:\"data\";s:2:\"11\";s:7:\"attribs\";a:0:{}s:8:\"xml_base\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"xml_base_explicit\";b:0;s:8:\"xml_lang\";s:0:\"\";}}}}}}}s:27:\"http://www.w3.org/2005/Atom\";a:1:{s:4:\"link\";a:1:{i:0;a:5:{s:4:\"data\";s:0:\"\";s:7:\"attribs\";a:1:{s:0:\"\";a:3:{s:4:\"href\";s:24:\"https://aioseo.com/feed/\";s:3:\"rel\";s:4:\"self\";s:4:\"type\";s:19:\"application/rss+xml\";}}s:8:\"xml_base\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"xml_base_explicit\";b:0;s:8:\"xml_lang\";s:0:\"\";}}}s:44:\"http://purl.org/rss/1.0/modules/syndication/\";a:2:{s:12:\"updatePeriod\";a:1:{i:0;a:5:{s:4:\"data\";s:9:\"\n	hourly	\";s:7:\"attribs\";a:0:{}s:8:\"xml_base\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"xml_base_explicit\";b:0;s:8:\"xml_lang\";s:0:\"\";}}s:1